## 5. Implementation in AI Prompts

When requesting image generation:

### ✅ CORRECT
```
Use the original logo from: [exact file path]
Use the original photo: [exact file path]
Reference image: [exact file path]
```

### ❌ INCORRECT
```
Generate a logo similar to...
Create a professional-looking portrait of Dmitry Kalashnik
Make it look like a Torah scholar with books
Based on this description of the logo...
```

